GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 15th May, 2007
25 Vaisakha, 1929 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 15th May,
2007 :-
Shri Dayanidhi Maran relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of Communications and Information Technology;
i)
ii)
Shri A. Raja relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of
Environment and Forests and assumed the charge of the office of
the Minister of Communications and Information Technology;
iii)
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of the
Minister of Environment and Forests; and
Shri S. Regupathy relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of State in the Ministry of Home Affairs and assumed the
charge of the office of the Minister of State in the Ministry of
Environment and Forests.
iv)
(K.L. Sharma)
